{"type": "article", "id": 15530, "title": "Bruvelo 咖啡机", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-25T06:30:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135550jbJ6KqIB5VHp7kux.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款智能咖啡机，通过智能手机或电脑上的 Bruvelo 专用 App 操作。它带有一个内置粉碎机和电子称，可以精确测量加入的咖啡豆和水的比例，只需用 App 设置水温和水粉比例，按下“brew”键，就可以等待一杯咖啡的诞生了。虽然外形并无特殊之处，但能快速生产一杯咖啡且毫不占用空间，专为上班人士准备。目前正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.bruvelo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里是产品主页</a>和<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bruvelo/bruvelo-simplify-and-elevate-your-coffee\" target=\"_blank\">众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142619qevBs59Ox2RXkGg6.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99266504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142619hvw16Vri9SP0DKW3.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142620kuay9DjInVMLJ7pi.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142620ENUumat9vgrTVZOl.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.46821516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}